user: That all sounds really impressive. I hope other fashion brands follow H&M's lead in adopting sustainable practices. What can we as consumers do to support sustainable fashion?
assistant: As consumers, there are several things we can do to support sustainable fashion:

1. Shop responsibly: One of the most effective ways to support sustainable fashion is to choose brands that prioritize sustainability. Look for eco-friendly materials, ethical labor practices, and sustainable production processes.

